Steps For BAckend

1.  initialize the firebase:- firebase init
2.  Choose Function, from given options
3.  Do some required stuff.
4.  Choose Language for cloud Function :- Here Choose , Javascript
5.  Install Dependecies , if asked then type (Y)

## After this whenever needed to install the pacjkages , then we have to move in the correct location using cd.

For Example here i want to install the express in index.js of Backed Function Folder ,
So First Of all we have to channge the directory to install the packages: cd Function.

After these all process:- 6. Install these three packages.
express, cors and stripe.
